ref="https://www.nme.com/news/music/cignature-continue-six-member-group-without-belle-3573467">讨论了她们的未来计划，</a>成员 Belle 将加入即将成立的女子组合<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/unis">UNIS</a> 。后者是通过韩国真人秀歌唱比赛<a href="https://www.nme.com/series/universe-ticket"><em>Universe Ticket</em></a>组建的，预计将活跃两年半。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/gi-dle-oddball-music-video-wife-3574709">(G)I-DLE 发布了他们的新歌《Wife》的古怪音乐视频，</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
